sshguard (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release
  * LSTM-based SSH intrusion detection with sequence modeling
  * Real-time log monitoring with hourly window feature extraction
  * Automatic IP blocking via iptables
  * Slow-rate and fast-rate attack detection
  * 9-feature model matching training pipeline
  * Sequence-based prediction (3-window sequences)
  * Cumulative num_failed_days tracking per IP
  * Source port extraction from log events
  * Detection threshold set to 0.7
  * Clean installation without duplicate dependencies

 -- SSHGuard Team <team@sshguard.local>  Sun, 12 Oct 2025 23:00:00 +0000
